name: Warriors of the Last Light  Version II V2

metadata.name: Aria | Warriors of the Last Light - Version II
metadata.description:
Aria's warrior strength lies in being able to shape the emitted frequencies of surrounding sonic sounds that may be used as a weapon against the warriors, turning these into melodious tunes.

In Version II of "Warriors of the Last Light," the original Genesis Collection is reimagined in a new light-- where the characters are depicted in anime/manga style.  
 
Size: 20"x20"  
DPI 300
